title: Clay and Buck’s Countdown to Election Day Episode 4 - Oct 16 2022

description:
Five fantastic candidates – Dr. Mehmet Oz (PA), Sen. Ron Johnson (WI), Christine Drazan (OR), Kelly Tshibaka (AK), and Adam Laxalt (NV) – plus election analysis from RNC chairwoman, Ronna McDaniel.
